name: veggie heist
description:
Veggie heist in 2100x2100px — hand-drawn digitally on procreate

First of all, the idea of veggie heist is pop-up because I watched children’s video ‘Veggie Garden’ where in the video it says that the vitamins were stolen by candy :)) they said, ‘candy is a pest’.

In this work, these 5 men are the pests! They want to stole veggies with the vitamins LOL
Pardon my description. Honestly, this is a spontaneous writing.

And, thank you for collect this work (this also collect my random thought)! That’s meant a lot ❤️
